      "title": "Archeology goes to the presidential palace",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A team from the Department of Archeology including the Commissioner of Archeology Professor Anura Manatunga has gone there today to investigate the damage to the properties in ancient places including the President's House occupied by the militants.",
        "Professor Anura Manatunga said that he hopes to review the facts observed there and make a statement regarding it today."
